{"tid":2047088,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"印度《Remove China Apps》熱爆　清除侵犯私隱 App 防監控","createTime":"2020-06-02T01:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T00:56:35.000Z","uid":267331,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7cbafb5403b39953d8b933af07cc95c53039f676","tid":2047088,"uid":267331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:12:58.000Z","msg":"由中國公司所開發的手機程式在過去一直被指存在資料外洩的風險，令不少手機用戶在過去避免下載相關程式。隨著中國與印度在近期因邊界問題而進一步加劇了印度的反華情緒，當地就有一間軟件公司免費於 Play Store 上推出了一個名為「移除中國程式 Remove China Apps」的程式，自推出後兩週內下載次數已多達 100 萬，反應熱烈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「移除中國程式」是由一間位於印度名為 OneTouch AppLabs 的公司所開發，自兩週前推出後於 Play Store 評分高達 4.8 分，並擁有 96,000 多個評論。據該程式的功能介紹，「移除中國程式」可以掃描並列出用戶手機上已安裝而且所有由中國公司開發的應用程式，讓用戶可以分辨出自己的裝置是否有資料外洩的機會並即時刪除相關程式。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n據當地媒體的報道，「移除中國程式」在使用時亦不需要讀取用戶於手機上的任何權限，故此不用擔心程式會接觸到用戶的個人信息，而且在使用時亦不會有廣告出現，使用方式十分簡單。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/06/01/remove-china-apps-races-to-1-million-downloads-within-two-weeks-as-anti-china-sentiment-gains-momentum/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F06%2F01%2Fremove-china-apps-races-to-1-million-downloads-within-two-weeks-as-anti-china-sentiment-gains-momentum%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbUKa%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=728e20d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/06/01/remove-china-apps-races-to-1-million-downloads-within-two-weeks-as-anti-china-sentiment-gains-momentum/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"3fed573f5d129060c8d2be677a5ffbadb471c067","tid":2047088,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:58:18.000Z","msg":"我都要下載<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fc77ba7f20fe190dc25de2b54adca12231b1ff","tid":2047088,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e